citation: Proclamation under the Motor Vehicle Traders Act 2011 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Motor Vehicle Traders Act 2011

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Motor Vehicle Traders Act 2011 fix 31 December 2011 as the day on which section 64(1) of, and Schedule 1 to, that Act commence.

19 December 2011

PETER G. UNDERWOOD

Governor

By His Excellency's Command,

NICK MCKIM

Minister for Corrections and Consumer Protection

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 28 December 2011

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Justice.
